snippet.title: RandomPac (Pac-Man arcade game remake) (by Luca Carminati, LC-Games)
snippet.description:
Download RandomPac from https://lowcarb.itch.io

RandomPac is a tribute to Pac-Man (Pakkuman), an arcade game released by Namco in 1980.
Main differences from the original version:
 - Randomly generated mazes
 - Bonus rounds

Author: Luca Carminati (lucacarminati1967@gmail.com)
